# Tools I Use for Work

This README contains a list of design and creative tools I frequently use for my work as a frontend developer with a designer mindset, along with links to their official websites.

## Design & Creative Tools

| Tool Name          | Description                      | Link                                   |
|--------------------|----------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| Figma              | Interface design tool            | [Figma](https://www.figma.com)         |
| Lucidchart         | Diagramming and flowchart tool   | [Lucidchart](https://www.lucidchart.com) |
| Adobe XD           | UI/UX design and prototyping tool | [Adobe XD](https://www.adobe.com/products/xd.html) |
| Canva              | Graphic design tool              | [Canva](https://www.canva.com)         |
| Sketch             | Vector graphics editor for UI/UX | [Sketch](https://www.sketch.com)       |
| InVision           | Prototyping and collaboration tool | [InVision](https://www.invisionapp.com) |
| Zeplin             | Handoff tool for designers and developers | [Zeplin](https://zeplin.io)           |
| Balsamiq           | Wireframing tool                 | [Balsamiq](https://balsamiq.com)       |
| Miro               | Online collaborative whiteboard  | [Miro](https://miro.com)               |
| Dribbble           | Design inspiration platform      | [Dribbble](https://dribbble.com)       |

## System Design & Diagramming Tools

| Tool Name          | Description                      | Link                                   |
|--------------------|----------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| Draw.io            | Diagramming tool for flowcharts, ER diagrams, etc. | [Draw.io](https://app.diagrams.net)   |
| Creately           | Diagramming and collaboration tool | [Creately](https://creately.com)       |
| Cacoo              | Online diagram and flowchart maker | [Cacoo](https://cacoo.com)             |
| Gliffy             | Diagramming tool for ER diagrams and system design | [Gliffy](https://www.gliffy.com)       |
| Whimsical          | Collaborative wireframes, flowcharts, mind maps    | [Whimsical](https://whimsical.com)    |
| Moqups             | Online tool for wireframes, mockups, and diagrams  | [Moqups](https://moqups.com)          |
| OmniGraffle        | Diagram design and ER modeling tool               | [OmniGraffle](https://www.omnigroup.com/omnigraffle) |
| ERDPlus            | Simple tool for creating ER diagrams               | [ERDPlus](https://erdplus.com)        |
| Visual Paradigm    | System modeling and diagram tool                 | [Visual Paradigm](https://www.visual-paradigm.com) |
| SmartDraw          | Diagramming tool for complex system design        | [SmartDraw](https://www.smartdraw.com) |

Feel free to click on the links to explore more about these tools.
